<view class="wrap">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="hero-title">极速去水印</view>
    <view class="hero-sub">粘贴分享链接，一键提取无水印视频 / 图片</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <textarea
      class="input"
      placeholder="把抖音 / 快手 / 小红书的分享文案粘贴到这里…"
      placeholder-class="ph"
      value="{{input}}"
      bindinput="onInput"
      maxlength="2000"
      auto-height
    />

    <view class="row spread mt-s" wx:if="{{detected}}">
      <view class="row gap">
        <text class="tag" wx:if="{{detected.supported}}">已识别 · {{detected.name}}</text>
        <text class="tag tag-warn" wx:else>暂不支持的链接</text>
      </view>
      <text class="link muted" bindtap="clearInput">清空</text>
    </view>

    <view class="row gap mt">
      <button class="btn btn-ghost flex1" bindtap="paste">粘贴链接</button>
      <button
        class="btn btn-primary flex2"
        bindtap="onParse"
        loading="{{parsing}}"
        disabled="{{parsing}}"
      >立即去水印</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <ad
    wx:if="{{bannerUnitId}}"
    class="banner"
    unit-id="{{bannerUnitId}}"
    ad-type="banner"
    ad-theme="white"
  ></ad>

  <view class="card mt">
    <view class="block-title">支持平台</view>
    <view class="chips">
      <text class="chip" wx:for="{{platforms}}" wx:key="*this">{{item}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="block-title mt">使用步骤</view>
    <view class="steps">
      <view class="step"><text class="step-n">1</text>在抖音等 App 点「分享 → 复制链接」</view>
      <view class="step"><text class="step-n">2</text>回到本程序，点「粘贴链接」</view>
      <view class="step"><text class="step-n">3</text>点「立即去水印」，看完广告即可保存</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="footnote muted center">
    本工具仅用于提取你有权使用的素材，请勿用于侵权用途。
  </view>
</view>
